OL,3,CNewcastle United head coach to remain
OL,4,Cat club
OL,6,FNewcastle United head coach Eddie Howe
OL,7,Fwill remain at the club into next
OL,8,Fseason, it has been announced.
OL,10,FIt follows crunch talks with the
OL,11,Fclub's owners amid a disappointing
OL,12,Fseason.
OL,14,FMany fans have questioned Howe's
OL,15,Ffuture on Tyneside as the club
OL,16,Fcurrently sits 13th in the Premier
OL,17,FLeague and has been knocked out of all
OL,18,Fcup competitions.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/2
