OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1777903640
OL,3,CNewcastle United head coach to remain
OL,4,Cat club
OL,6,FHowever, the owners from the Saudi
OL,7,FArabia Public Investment Fund (PIF)
OL,8,Fappear to have given the 48-year-old
OL,9,Ftheir backing ahead of a crucial
OL,10,Fsummer transfer window.
OL,12,FSupporters will be hoping that
OL,13,FSaturday's 3-1 win against Brighton
OL,14,Fmarks a turnaround in the team's form,
OL,15,Fhaving suffered 16 Premier League
OL,16,Fdefeats so far this season.
OL,18,FHowe admitted "pressure" had built in
OL,19,Fthe run up to the match, with the head
OL,20,Fcoach suffering arguably his toughest
OL,21,Fperiod since joining the club in 2021.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/2
